{"text": "If you're somehow into tower-defense or remotely liked DW1 then DW2 is absolutely recommended unless you can't stand this level of graphics. It is basically DW1 with everything made better except the visuals. And it's still a ton of fun! This is one of those \"just that one more (level, item, skill, mastery...) and then I'll stop\"-games :-) Definately the best 2D-TD-game. And if 2D/3D won't matter to you, it may even be the best TD-game.", "appid": "698540", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992813688", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "24", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530878400.0}
