{"text": "First of all [Notice: At the request of the publisher, RESIDENT EVIL RESISTANCE is unlisted on the Steam store and will not appear in search.] That alone is pathetic and horribly disgusting. A brilliant idea quickly turned into a shameful project on its way to abandonware.  That game itself is fun, when the servers decide they want to work, but it also boils down to who gets the upper hand first.  Little to no communication, No diversity in levels and placement (which you WANT to shake up because masterminds memorize these things), You know how boring it is to play a game as a mastermind when we already know were all the spawn locations are no matter how you set up the map?  This game has so much, SO MUCH, potential. But you dont listen to us, you dont communicate with us, and now you've taken the game off steam. Thats not how you handle a game. Especially with this one. Its been a very long time since we had a game introduce some of these mechanics and with a franchise we all love. Frankly the dev's need to get there rear ends in gear and toughen up.   Ill revise my review and recommend this game once it returns were it belongs, On the steam Store Listing And do yourself a favor, Get rid of the micro transaction BS. You dont need it and theres no way any of us would funnel money into a game as long as you treat your project like this. doesn't make any of us confident to entrust investing in you as a whole.", "appid": "952070", "steamid": "profiles/76561198030096699", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "2", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1594382400.0}
{"text": "Angry Girl é um jogo de plataforma bem simples e curto. Nele você é uma garota bem brava, não se sabe porque, você só é assim mesmo. E sai matando todos os inimigos que aparecem na sua frente, e eles são um grupo de esqueletos, de cyborgs e vampiros.  É um jogo que não oferece nenhum desafio, eu diria que é só pra passar o tempo, ou nem tanto, já que você vai encerrar rapidinho. Talvez futuramente ele seja um jogo bom para aqueles que gostam de jogos fáceis para platinar, atualmente suas conquistas não entram em nenhuma contagem. Por agora eu não recomendo o jogo, se fosse um jogo de graça tudo bem ser assim simples, mas ele é pago e logo não vale o tanto que você gasta para jogar quase nada.", "appid": "1113500", "steamid": "profiles/76561198146770117", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1566043200.0}
{"text": ": -  There are no customizable control sets. -  Combat physics are basically non existent and the AI is plain dumb.  -  Command input responsiveness is a game of luck in context situations, in the hacking mechanics as well as in the menu -  Only about 40% of cutscene dialogs are recorded or play at all -  Texture glitches in cutscenes and ingame -  Jumping is only context-sensitive -  close to no character facial animation -  you can basically buy any item from the invenotry which has no space limit -  Augmentation menu is cut down to a few augs/augtrees -  oh and only about 2 hours of gameplay, ending in a cliff hanger that smacks the 10€ you paid at your face, telling you to come back to throw more money at this ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥. :: +  I know now I don't have to buy anything more from this developer +  The torture was over in only 2 hours (my 8hours gaming time mostly come from idling) +  It did not price you at AAA-Level + if you took the limited offer you get one of the best games in gaming history \"Deus Ex GOTY\" with your purchase. If you have that already, avoid this piece of feces.", "appid": "258180", "steamid": "profiles/76561197971374952", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "11", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1395576000.0}
