{"text": "I used to play this game alot, then i decided to look at the forums and realised its simply toxic in there, this game was being developed by a few individuals and for whatever reason they decided to start taking advice from one of their players as to how the game should be \"balanced\", lets just say from that moment on the game became this small groups private playground as they constantly match up with noobs and post themselves bragging about how they are the best and acting as though it requires skill to get many kills agaisnt people who havent had the game tweaked to their benefit. The main culprit for this games downfall is a douche by the name of Flavio, he singlehandedly chased away anyone from the forums who disagrees with him, as he professes himself to be the king of this dead game. ego tripping aside this game could be excelent if the devs handed it over to professionals to develop or/and stopped taking the advice of egocentric kids.", "appid": "214420", "steamid": "profiles/76561197973647025", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1465041600.0}
{"text": "Вам нужно психологическая разрядка? Хотите подумать о вечном? Наслодится видом горы? Тогда эта игра для Вас! Вся суть симулятора горы заключается в том, что вы включаете её на полный экран и садатись подальше наблюдать за ней. Она крутится, крутится и... крутится. Вокруг летают облака, а иногда даже метеоритный дождь. В общем это одно из самых бестолковых вложений денег... хоть и не такое большое Но ведь кому то нравится смотреть на горы? p.s. после покупки запускал ровно один раз", "appid": "313340", "steamid": "profiles/76561198046042990", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1475582400.0}
{"text": "Проходил ограбления, накопил херову тучу денег, прилетел бан навсегда. <3", "appid": "271590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198204776264", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1446552000.0}
{"text": "It tries hard but never succeeds. It throws at you some lovecraftian stuff but makes it in a comedy way. And even in this it fails miserably. The whole humour seems to be more teenagers-orientated and not really funny. You can't just take some lovecraftian terms, mix them with lazy students chit-chat and be done with it, it just doesn't make it together.   It tries to be more than a kinetic VN: it introduces a new mechanic: click-to-interact, but even this aspect is totally linear. You just click on every piece from left to right and be done with it. One more fail. The story starts very slowly. It shows you tons of characters but most of them seem to exist for the single purpose of being \"funny\". The story ends quite abruptly and doesn't reveal any motivation behind the characters. It just throws facts at you. The protagonist is stupid as hell, but at least it is said in the plain text. Technically it also has some flaws. The most part of text is written in caps which is more difficult to read, Steam overlay doesn't work (you can't make screenshots the usual way). The menus are also quite poor-made, there is no settings, no coming back and almost no sounds. At least the art is made well.  I know this game was on Kickstarter and they promised it to be completely different: a platformer shooter or something. Seems like there were some big problems with development team. Maybe that's why the game is cut off and not polished.", "appid": "870290", "steamid": "profiles/76561198071848932", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "13", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1589544000.0}
{"text": "It’s not broken: multiplayer doesn’t work online, but you can play it via LAN or VPN. However, I’d say it’s not worth the effort. The game is very short (30-40 minutes), doesn’t have any interesting puzzles, story or good combat. Feels like a tech demo more than anything.", "appid": "468560", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992892379", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581854400.0}
